{"tid":1196444,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"第一次企前面 第一次同個盾鬥力 少少感想","createTime":"2019-06-09T19:43:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T16:39:34.000Z","uid":213607,"like":79,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d05931f6699dac16a30f75324ae6b3199d4ffbe3","tid":1196444,"uid":213607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T19:43:56.000Z","msg":"各位衝既勇武 辛苦曬你地 真係體會到嗰種勇武所需要既意志同體力<br />\n小妹不才 平時冇好好鍛鍊體能 攞住部機頂四五波就要做逃兵<br />\n因為戴住個罩透唔到氣 又推到攰<br />\n原諒我提早撤退<br />\n總結到既係平時做開占既好力好氣巴絲比狗迫既時候真係要靠你地既身體去擋<br />\n而個罩亦一定要梳爽 唔好睇少需要消耗既體力 唔係下下有位你退一個唔小心就比人的走冇力求生<br />\n<br />\n最後想同仲留守既講聲各位請繼續加油 趁有力占多啲地 比休息完翻黎既我地接力守"},{"pid":"d38aeff680ea106fac48b31d5eb08855836b283e","tid":1196444,"uid":213607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T19:51:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26c08daa22ac48297a7139f6c30adf40050c250c","tid":1196444,"uid":140432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T20:00:47.000Z","msg":"辛苦你了"},{"pid":"d91d3dd8334649e6d17f8e70647b5a4d33b2ca27","tid":1196444,"uid":213607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"26c08daa22ac48297a7139f6c30adf40050c250c","tid":1196444,"uid":140432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T20:00:47.000Z","msg":"辛苦你了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T20:04:27.000Z","msg":"更多人更辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4b894ea5e0b51fd050bb5424554661b58f15018","tid":1196444,"uid":213607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T20:15:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a14c3237d415ea51a4f42be7631e9d888b46a3a7","tid":1196444,"uid":167426,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T20:20:34.000Z","msg":"女仔敢企最前真係要致以崇高嘅敬意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />